From: Mathieu Baudier <mbaudier@argeo.org>
Date: Tue, 17 Jun 2025 15:49:51 +0200
Subject: fix-pkg-config

Add prefix variables to libdir and includedir in llama.pc.in
---
 cmake/llama.pc.in | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/cmake/llama.pc.in b/cmake/llama.pc.in
index d63dd17..56d46c9 100644
--- a/cmake/llama.pc.in
+++ b/cmake/llama.pc.in
@@ -1,7 +1,7 @@
 prefix=@CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX@
 exec_prefix=@CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX@
-libdir=@LLAMA_LIB_INSTALL_DIR@
-includedir=@LLAMA_INCLUDE_INSTALL_DIR@
+libdir=${exec_prefix}/@LLAMA_LIB_INSTALL_DIR@
+includedir=${prefix}/@LLAMA_INCLUDE_INSTALL_DIR@
 
 Name: llama
 Description: Port of Facebook's LLaMA model in C/C++
